<DocsLayout 
    title="rugbyclaw results" 
    description="View recent rugby match results">
    
    <p class="lead">View recent rugby match results with personality-driven summaries</p>

    <h2>Usage</h2>
    <pre><code>rugbyclaw results [league] [options]</code></pre>

    <h2>Examples</h2>
    
    <h3>View all recent results</h3>
    <pre><code>rugbyclaw results</code></pre>
    <p>Shows recent results across all your favorite leagues.</p>

    <h3>Filter by league</h3>
    <pre><code>rugbyclaw results top14
rugbyclaw results premiership
rugbyclaw results six_nations</code></pre>

    <h2>Options</h2>
    <table>
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Option</th>
                <th>Description</th>
                <th>Default</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td><code>--json</code></td>
                <td>Output as JSON</td>
                <td>false</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><code>--days</code></td>
                <td>Number of days back</td>
                <td>7</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>Match Summaries</h2>
    <p>Results include personality-driven summaries based on the outcome:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Big wins:</strong> "Absolute clinic. That wasn't a match, that was a statement."</li>
        <li><strong>Close wins:</strong> "Heart attack rugby. Clenched the whole second half."</li>
        <li><strong>Losses:</strong> "Let's not talk about it. Pain. Moving on."</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Tips</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Check Monday mornings for weekend results</li>
        <li>Use <code>--days 14</code> for two weeks of history</li>
        <li>Combine with <code>rugbyclaw team last</code> for specific teams</li>
    </ul>

